Description:
Suddenly, your ship enters a large whirlpool and is slowly engulfed by it.

The ship is breaking apart and pieces of wood begin to fly through the air, cutting everything in their path.

The water is freezing, but it's still the best option if you don't want to be swallowed by the whirlpool along with what's left of the ship.
DescriptionAction: You can only jump into the water and try to swim quickly to shore.
